1. We recommend that you use the Atom text editor for this course.
    We prefer it because it works the same on Windows, Macintosh, and Linux.
    All of the course demonstration videos use Atom. You can download and install it from:

    https://atom.io/

2. Là nộp bài tập trên đây : 
This course uses a third-party tool, Python Code Playground
    https://www.py4e.com/tsugi/store/ (https://www.py4e.com/tsugi/store/details/pythonauto)